{"tid":1593501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送頭論。連登仔係懦弱，懦夫","createTime":"2019-09-25T05:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:27:57.000Z","uid":12773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"097e0c7fe8b8f84cb40b12e054cb752dfc64c49e","tid":1593501,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"警犬濫捕<br />\n目的係捉到你驚，捉到你怕，捉到你唔敢出黎<br />\n而連登仔既真面目<br />\n就係順民<br />\n因為怕被濫捕<br />\n因為自己的懦弱<br />\n就本末倒置<br />\n將被濫捕的義士稱為送頭<br />\n反而不去譴責警犬濫捕<br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位義士<br />\n每次行動前必須計劃好逃走路線<br />\n以防被濫捕<br />\n<br />\n而各位懦弱既連登仔<br />\n切勿再用送頭去形容義士<br />\n來掩飾你係一個怕被濫捕的懦夫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20663210e981ccc9495eed22e10ea39a8164898d","tid":1593501,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"3591b67c20d7892d63c845fa2dad75cf570dc8d1","tid":1593501,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.